	3.Excercise: Your program takes a user input which is a number. Let's call this number n. 
	Then an array with the size of n should be created, which contains the word "Salam" in each cell.
	
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		
		int i = 0;
		Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
		int n = sc.nextInt();
		
		String[] items = new String[n];
		items[i] = " Salam";
	
		
		for( i = 0; i < n; i++) {
			System.out.print("Salam"+" ");
			}
		}
	}
